---
import ThankYouLayout from '../../layouts/ThankYouLayout.astro';
---

<ThankYouLayout
  productSlug="sovereignty-assessment-toolkit"
  description="Your Sovereignty Assessment Toolkit is ready to download."
  readyLine="Your Sovereignty Assessment Toolkit is ready."
  downloadHeading="Download your toolkit"
  downloadHref="/downloads/Sovereignty-Assessment-Toolkit-v1.0.pdf"
>
  <Fragment slot="download-description">
    <p>The Sovereignty Assessment Toolkit is a 47-point structured self-assessment across seven domains: Transparency, Autonomy, Invitation, Dignity, Silence, Data Sovereignty, and AI &amp; Voice.</p>
    <p>It takes about 90 minutes to complete - or start with the 6 Red Flag Items in 5 minutes.</p>
  </Fragment>

  <Fragment slot="next-steps">
    <a href="/products/sovereignty-toolkit" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Run the assessment</h3>
      <p>Set aside 90 minutes. Be honest. The value is in the truth, not the score.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Open the toolkit page &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/consulting" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Go deeper</h3>
      <p>If the assessment surfaces structural questions, a Sovereignty-Honoring Design Workshop or Privacy Architecture Review can help.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">See engagement options &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/fit" class="pd-upsell-card">
      <h3>Check your fit</h3>
      <p>A 5-minute fit assessment to see which Evoke services align with where you are right now.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Take the assessment &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a href="https://cal.com/cal.com-evoked/discovery-call" class="pd-upsell-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <h3>Talk it through</h3>
      <p>Book a free 30-minute discovery call to discuss your results.</p>
      <span class="pd-upsell-link">Schedule &rarr;</span>
    </a>
  </Fragment>
</ThankYouLayout>
